The '''Ando Project''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] operation to harvest [[Andoan mineral-fish]] to provide a cheap method of extracting minerals essential to the production of [[Laser/Legends|laser]] weapons.

==History==
The ''[[Bountiful]]'' collected the fish, which were then transferred to the [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] [[Eclipse (freighter)|''Eclipse'']] where they were processed and shipped to [[Uridia]]. Once there, the fish were placed in special tanks and adapted to process [[uridium]] from the Uridian soil.
[[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Amarith]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] was tipped off to the Imperial operation on [[Ando/Legends|Ando]], and led a team of Alliance agents from [[Chiron Base]] to disrupt the project.

